(clarifying,clarified,clarifies) 

1. V-T To clarify something means to make it easier to understand, usually by explaining it in more detail. 澄清 [正式] 

例： Thank you for writing and allowing me to clarify the present position. 谢谢你来信并允许我澄清目前的状况。 

